---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: All Golf. No Math.
description: Marker tracks scores live, manages your side games, and settles the tab instantly. Available on iPhone, iPad, Android, and Web.
---

{% from "components/badges.njk" import AppStoreBadge, PlayStoreBadge %}
{% from "components/platform-bar.njk" import PlatformSupportBar %}
{% from "components/trust-stats.njk" import TrustStats %}

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero__content">
    <h1>All Golf.<br>No Math.</h1>
    <p class="hero__sub">Live scoring, side games, and instant settlement for your whole group.</p>
    <div class="hero__actions">
      <a href="https://app.marker.golf" class="btn btn-primary">Try Marker Free</a>
    </div>
    <p class="hero__pricing-note">{{ pricing.heroNote }}</p>
    <div class="hero__screenshot">
      <img src="{{ '/images/screen-home.png' | url }}" alt="Marker scorecard on iPhone" width="320" height="690" loading="eager">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Platform bar -->
{{ PlatformSupportBar() }}

<!-- Trust stats -->
{{ TrustStats() }}

<!-- Pricing -->
<section class="section pricing" id="pricing">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="pricing__header">
      <h2>{{ pricing.header.heading }}</h2>
      <p>{{ pricing.header.subheading }}</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pricing__grid">

      {% for plan in pricing.plans %}
      <div class="pricing-card pricing-card--{{ plan.id }}">
        <p class="pricing-card__plan">{{ plan.name }}</p>
        <div class="pricing-card__price">
          <span class="pricing-card__amount">{{ plan.amount }}</span>
          {% if plan.period %}<span class="pricing-card__period">{{ plan.period }}</span>{% endif %}
        </div>
        <p class="pricing-card__alt">{{ plan.altText }}</p>
        <div class="pricing-card__divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <ul class="pricing-card__features">
          {% for feature in plan.features %}
          <li>{{ feature }}</li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
        {% if plan.cta %}
        <a href="{{ plan.cta.href }}" class="btn btn-ghost">{{ plan.cta.text }}</a>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      {% endfor %}

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- How it works -->
<section class="section section--white how-it-works">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header" style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:48px;">
      <h2>Set up in under a minute.</h2>
      <p style="max-width:420px; margin-inline:auto; margin-top:12px;">No spreadsheets. No mental math. Just tap and play.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="how-it-works__grid">
      <div class="how-card">
        <div class="how-card__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
            <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Invite your group</h3>
        <p>Share a link and your playing partners join instantly — no accounts required.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="how-card">
        <div class="how-card__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 20h9"/>
            <path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Enter scores live</h3>
        <p>Everyone scores on their own device. The leaderboard updates in real time, hole by hole.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="how-card">
        <div class="how-card__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/>
            <path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Settle up instantly</h3>
        <p>Skins, Nassau, Nines — Marker calculates exactly who owes who. No arguments, no guesswork.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Feature: Live leaderboard -->
<section class="section feature-showcase">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="feature-row">
      <div class="feature-row__text">
        <h2>A live leaderboard everyone can see.</h2>
        <p>Every player's phone shows the same real-time standings. No more waiting until the 19th hole to find out who's winning.</p>
        <a href="https://app.marker.golf" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Try it free</a>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-row__media">
        <img src="{{ '/images/screen-leaderboard.png' | url }}" alt="Live leaderboard on Marker" width="280" height="560" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-row feature-row--flip">
      <div class="feature-row__text">
        <h2>Every side game, already built in.</h2>
        <p>Skins, Nassau, Matchplay, Nines, Stableford — pick your games before teeing off and Marker tracks every dollar automatically.</p>
        <a href="{{ '/games/' | url }}" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">See all games</a>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-row__media">
        <img src="{{ '/images/screen-games.png' | url }}" alt="Side games on Marker" width="280" height="560" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Commissioner callout -->
<section class="section commissioner-callout">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="commissioner-callout__header">
      <h2>Running a league or event?</h2>
      <p>Marker gives commissioners complete control — from flights and pairings to automatic settlements. One commissioner brings their entire group.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="commissioner-features">
      <div class="commissioner-feature">
        <div class="commissioner-feature__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Flights &amp; Pairings</h4>
        <p>Organize players into flights, build pairings, and manage the field before you reach the first tee.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="commissioner-feature">
        <div class="commissioner-feature__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <line x1="4" y1="21" x2="4" y2="14"/><line x1="4" y1="10" x2="4" y2="3"/><line x1="12" y1="21" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="3"/><line x1="20" y1="21" x2="20" y2="16"/><line x1="20" y1="12" x2="20" y2="3"/><line x1="1" y1="14" x2="7" y2="14"/><line x1="9" y1="8" x2="15" y2="8"/><line x1="17" y1="16" x2="23" y2="16"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Handicap Settings</h4>
        <p>Configure handicap rules per event. USGA-compliant calculations are built in automatically.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="commissioner-feature">
        <div class="commissioner-feature__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Live Leaderboards</h4>
        <p>Every player sees real-time standings on their own device throughout the entire round.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="commissioner-feature">
        <div class="commissioner-feature__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Team Competitions</h4>
        <p>Ryder Cup, Scotch, Team Stroke Play — full team format support for any size event.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="commissioner-feature">
        <div class="commissioner-feature__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Side Games for All</h4>
        <p>Nassau, Skins, Matchplay — run multiple games simultaneously across the entire field.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="commissioner-feature">
        <div class="commissioner-feature__icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Automatic Settlements</h4>
        <p>When the round ends, Marker calculates exactly who owes who. No disputes, no mental math.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="commissioner-callout__actions">
      <a href="{{ '/commissioners/' | url }}" class="btn btn-ghost">See commissioner tools</a>
      <a href="https://app.marker.golf" class="btn btn-primary">Set Up Your League</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- CTA band -->
<section class="cta-band">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Available anywhere you play.</h2>
    <p>iPhone, iPad, Android, Web — Marker is on every device in your group.</p>
    <div class="cta-band__actions">
      <a href="https://app.marker.golf" class="btn btn-primary">Try Marker Free</a>
      <div class="cta-band__badges">
        {{ AppStoreBadge() }}
        {{ PlayStoreBadge() }}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
